JetV looked to Artemis.  "Well in the words of Optimus Prime 
himself.  'Roll out'" JetV said quite loudly transforming into his ATV 
mode and burning through the room into the halls with Artemis 
hopefully behind him.

Slag looked baffled at these orders.  "Protect Technobots.  So you 
do know we stronger, and there forbetter. Ha yes!"

Crotale looked tp Pacifix. "Right"  He then thought to himself.  "He 
seems to know what he is doing, almost.  But I fear with his 
compassion he will soon show weaknesses in battle.  That's where 
i will help, for if one thing is more important to me then beating the 
tar out of a Pred, it's Pacifix beside me doing it."
